 />\n尤其學生有進步 果種滿足感無得輸<br />\n<br />\n我個位唔洗企 其他同事都唔洗點企法<br />\n前線體力勞動辛苦<br />\nADMIN對電腦對到悶<br />\n<br />\n24K"},{"pid":"0cad89aac768ea388d9c325de29708e17192a60d","tid":47214,"uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲人知唔知自己同其他人唔同？</blockquote><br />\n每一個人都同其他人唔同 唔係咩?"},{"pid":"da5fb046314b764935e2cad9f5bb41d477cac690","tid":47214,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"自己服務嘅對象多數幾多歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c333f92012d0989e2b9ba3ac1c70bb333a2654","tid":47214,"uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己服務嘅對象多數幾多歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6-18<br />\n十二年學制"},{"pid":"745768c5ff9b92ebb25cfcd288cd51aa5c6f87d6","tid":47214,"uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己服務嘅對象多數幾多歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6-18<br />\n十二年學制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWeb版回唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122adb6591c3555eeaf7e989a4e5ca1468953a05","tid":47214,"uid":10579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"我都讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過兩年就出黎教<br />\n想知呢行會唔會好辛苦<br />\n有冇啲野好難handle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d38d155bc0c14f30f5e9d9097fadffdcd73962","tid":47214,"uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=